 unresolved mid-infrared spectroscopy. We\nhighlight the need for including more complex chemistry when interpreting\nsolid-state spectroscopic observations of the inner regions of discs, and for\nconsidering dynamical aspects for future studies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Jul 2020 09:53:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-05"}
